data.description: Nestled on a peaceful dead-end street, this all brick ranch has a full, partially finished walk-out basement ready for your personal touch! This home has three bedrooms and three full bathrooms, and a spacious living room. The kitchen has granite countertops with a breakfast bar that is open to the family room that features a cozy fireplace. The deck overlooks the spacious yard, and the two car detached  garage. This is a lovely home for one-floor living, and still has ample space in the basement. Schedule your showing today!
